A SCANDAL IN BOHEMIA

5
00:00:10,629 --> 00:00:14,169
I.

6
00:00:14,170 --> 00:00:17,630
To Sherlock Holmes she is always THE woman.

7
00:00:17,630 --> 00:00:19,750
I have seldom heard him mention her under

8
