00:12:40,629 --> 00:12:45,399
A slow and heavy step, which had been heard

308
00:12:45,399 --> 00:12:48,139
upon the stairs and in the passage, paused

309
00:12:48,139 --> 00:12:50,529
immediately outside the door.

