322
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:21,920
cloak which was thrown over his shoulders

323
00:13:21,920 --> 00:13:24,760
was lined with flame-coloured silk and

324
00:13:24,759 --> 00:13:27,139
secured at the neck with a brooch which

