337
00:13:59,740 --> 00:14:01,760
From the lower part of the face he appeared

338
00:14:01,759 --> 00:14:04,519
to be a man of strong character, with a

339
00:14:04,519 --> 00:14:07,509
thick, hanging lip, and a long, straight

340
00:14:07,509 --> 00:14:10,359
chin suggestive of resolution pushed to the

341
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:13,200
length of obstinacy.

342
00:14:13,199 --> 00:14:16,369
"You had my note?" he asked with a deep

343
00:14:16,369 --> 00:14:18,909
harsh voice and a strongly marked German

344
00:14:18,910 --> 00:14:20,220
accent.

345
00:14:20,220 --> 00:14:21,980
"I told you that I would call."

346
00:14:23,230 --> 00:14:26,100
He looked from one to the other of us, as

347
00:14:26,100 --> 00:14:29,170
if uncertain which to address.

348
00:14:29,170 --> 00:14:31,050
"Pray take a seat," said Holmes.

349
00:14:31,899 --> 00:14:34,349
"This is my friend and colleague, Dr.

350
00:14:34,350 --> 00:14:36,890
Watson, who is occasionally good enough to

351
00:14:36,889 --> 00:14:38,689
