369
00:15:27,329 --> 00:15:30,329
at the end of that time the matter will be

370
00:15:30,329 --> 00:15:31,319
of no importance.

371
00:15:32,279 --> 00:15:34,889
At present it is not too much to say that

372
00:15:34,889 --> 00:15:37,639
it is of such weight it may have an

373
00:15:37,639 --> 00:15:41,509
influence upon European history."

374
00:15:41,509 --> 00:15:44,509
"I promise," said Holmes.

375
00:15:44,509 --> 00:15:46,379
"And I."

376
00:15:46,379 --> 00:15:49,409
"You will excuse this mask," continued our

377
00:15:49,410 --> 00:15:50,360
strange visitor.

378
00:15:51,199 --> 00:15:53,939
"The august person who employs me wishes

379
00:15:53,939 --> 00:15:57,169
his agent to be unknown to you, and I may

380
00:15:57,170 --> 00:15:59,550
confess at once that the title by which I

381
00:15:59,550 --> 00:16:02,500
have just called myself is not exactly my

382
00:16:02,499 --> 00:16:02,749
