462
00:19:41,090 --> 00:19:43,530
"Was there a secret marriage?"

463
00:19:43,529 --> 00:19:44,729
"None."

464
00:19:44,730 --> 00:19:48,380
"No legal papers or certificates?"

465
00:19:48,380 --> 00:19:49,550
