472
00:20:05,370 --> 00:20:06,310
Forgery."

473
00:20:06,309 --> 00:20:08,489
"My private note-paper."

474
00:20:08,490 --> 00:20:09,120
"Stolen."

475
00:20:09,120 --> 00:20:12,650
"My own seal."

476
00:20:12,649 --> 00:20:14,429
"Imitated."

477
00:20:14,429 --> 00:20:16,049
"My photograph."

478
00:20:16,049 --> 00:20:17,839
"Bought."

479
00:20:17,840 --> 00:20:20,720
"We were both in the photograph."

480
00:20:20,720 --> 00:20:22,190
"Oh, dear!

481
00:20:22,190 --> 00:20:24,320
That is very bad!

482
00:20:24,320 --> 00:20:26,360
Your Majesty has indeed committed an

483
00:20:26,360 --> 00:20:27,220
indiscretion."

484
00:20:27,220 --> 00:20:32,150
"I was mad--insane."

485
00:20:32,149 --> 00:20:35,509
"You have compromised yourself seriously."

486
00:20:35,510 --> 00:20:37,700
"I was only Crown Prince then.

487
00:20:37,700 --> 00:20:38,840
I was young.

488
00:20:38,840 --> 00:20:41,960
I am but thirty now."

489
00:20:41,960 --> 00:20:44,010
"It must be recovered."

490
00:20:44,010 --> 00:20:47,230
"We have tried and failed."

