00:21:34,220 --> 00:21:38,430
"I am about to be married."

515
00:21:38,429 --> 00:21:41,679
"So I have heard."

516
00:21:41,679 --> 00:21:44,399
"To Clotilde Lothman von Saxe-Meningen,

517
00:21:44,399 --> 00:21:47,609
second daughter of the King of Scandinavia.

518
00:21:47,610 --> 00:21:49,840
