523
00:22:00,799 --> 00:22:03,549
"And Irene Adler?"

524
00:22:03,549 --> 00:22:05,229
"Threatens to send them the photograph.

525
00:22:05,230 --> 00:22:07,710
And she will do it.

526
00:22:07,710 --> 00:22:09,610
I know that she will do it.

527
00:22:09,610 --> 00:22:13,040
You do not know her, but she has a soul of

528
00:22:13,039 --> 00:22:13,549
steel.

529
00:22:13,549 --> 00:22:15,389
She has the face of the most beautiful of

530
00:22:15,389 --> 00:22:18,379
women, and the mind of the most resolute of

531
00:22:18,380 --> 00:22:18,630
men.

532
00:22:19,600 --> 00:22:21,750
