533
00:22:21,750 --> 00:22:23,930
there are no lengths to which she would not

534
00:22:23,929 --> 00:22:26,539
go--none."

535
00:22:26,539 --> 00:22:28,589
"You are sure that she has not sent it

536
00:22:28,590 --> 00:22:29,010
yet?"

537
00:22:29,010 --> 00:22:32,390
"I am sure."

538
00:22:32,389 --> 00:22:33,689
"And why?"

539
00:22:33,690 --> 00:22:35,980
"Because she has said that she would send

540
00:22:35,980 --> 00:22:38,290
