541
00:22:38,289 --> 00:22:40,069
publicly proclaimed.

542
00:22:40,070 --> 00:22:42,600
That will be next Monday."

543
00:22:42,600 --> 00:22:46,570
"Oh, then we have three days yet," said

544
00:22:46,570 --> 00:22:47,930
Holmes with a yawn.

