681
00:28:17,110 --> 00:28:21,010
biographies I was compelled to listen to."

682
00:28:21,009 --> 00:28:22,929
"And what of Irene Adler?"

683
00:28:22,929 --> 00:28:24,659
I asked.

684
00:28:24,659 --> 00:28:27,049
"Oh, she has turned all the men's heads

685
00:28:27,049 --> 00:28:28,959
