692
00:28:44,269 --> 00:28:46,479
Seldom goes out at other times, except when

693
00:28:46,480 --> 00:28:47,830
she sings.

694
00:28:47,830 --> 00:28:50,410
Has only one male visitor, but a good deal

695
00:28:50,409 --> 00:28:50,759
of him.

696
00:28:51,490 --> 00:28:54,350
He is dark, handsome, and dashing, never

697
00:28:54,350 --> 00:28:56,960
calls less than once a day, and often

698
00:28:56,960 --> 00:28:58,260
twice.

699
00:28:58,259 --> 00:29:01,389
He is a Mr. Godfrey Norton, of the Inner

700
00:29:01,389 --> 00:29:03,159
Temple.

701
00:29:03,159 --> 00:29:05,149
See the advantages of a cabman as a

702
00:29:05,149 --> 00:29:06,869
confidant.

703
00:29:06,870 --> 00:29:09,310
They had driven him home a dozen times from

704
00:29:09,309 --> 00:29:12,129
Serpentine-mews, and knew all about him.

705
00:29:12,960 --> 00:29:14,670
When I had listened to all they had to

706
00:29:14,669 --> 00:29:17,379
tell, I began to walk up and down near

707
00:29:17,379 --> 00:29:20,199
Briony Lodge once more, and to think over

708
00:29:20,200 --> 00:29:22,860
my plan of campaign.

709
00:29:22,860 --> 00:29:25,530
"This Godfrey Norton was evidently an

710
00:29:25,529 --> 00:29:28,029
important factor in the matter.

711
00:29:28,029 --> 00:29:29,779
He was a lawyer.

712
00:29:29,779 --> 00:29:30,809
That sounded ominous.

713
00:29:31,649 --> 00:29:34,639
What was the relation between them, and

714
00:29:34,639 --> 00:29:37,589
what the object of his repeated visits?

715
00:29:37,590 --> 00:29:41,240
Was she his client, his friend, or his

716
00:29:41,240 --> 00:29:41,630
mistress?

717
00:29:42,779 --> 00:29:45,379
If the former, she had probably transferred

718
00:29:45,379 --> 00:29:47,649
