773
00:32:02,210 --> 00:32:04,840
I was just balancing whether I should run

774
00:32:04,840 --> 00:32:07,230
for it, or whether I should perch behind

775
00:32:07,230 --> 00:32:09,500
her landau when a cab came through the

776
00:32:09,499 --> 00:32:09,849
street.

777
00:32:10,710 --> 00:32:13,060
The driver looked twice at such a shabby

778
00:32:13,059 --> 00:32:14,769
fare, but I jumped in before he could

779
00:32:14,769 --> 00:32:15,209
object.

780
00:32:15,210 --> 00:32:18,620
'The Church of St. Monica,' said I, 'and

781
00:32:18,620 --> 00:32:20,970
half a sovereign if you reach it in twenty

782
00:32:20,970 --> 00:32:21,220
minutes.'

