784
00:32:24,169 --> 00:32:26,029
of course it was clear enough what was in

785
00:32:26,029 --> 00:32:27,249
the wind.

786
00:32:27,249 --> 00:32:29,009
"My cabby drove fast.

787
00:32:29,539 --> 00:32:32,299
I don't think I ever drove faster, but the

788
00:32:32,299 --> 00:32:35,089
others were there before us.

789
00:32:35,090 --> 00:32:36,770
The cab and the landau with their steaming

790
00:32:36,769 --> 00:32:38,769
horses were in front of the door when I

791
00:32:38,769 --> 00:32:39,399
arrived.

