00:32:39,399 --> 00:32:42,399
I paid the man and hurried into the church.

793
00:32:42,399 --> 00:32:45,579
There was not a soul there save the two

794
00:32:45,580 --> 00:32:47,730
whom I had followed and a surpliced

795
00:32:47,730 --> 00:32:50,630
clergyman, who seemed to be expostulating

796
00:32:50,629 --> 00:32:51,849
