00:33:09,850 --> 00:33:11,850
"'Thank God,' he cried.

806
00:33:11,850 --> 00:33:12,720
'You'll do.

807
00:33:12,720 --> 00:33:13,290
Come!

808
00:33:13,289 --> 00:33:14,939
Come!'

