00:33:14,940 --> 00:33:16,020
"'What then?'

810
00:33:16,019 --> 00:33:17,739
I asked.

811
00:33:17,740 --> 00:33:20,260
"'Come, man, come, only three minutes, or

812
00:33:20,259 --> 00:33:21,179
it won't be legal.'

813
00:33:22,169 --> 00:33:25,269
